{
  "texts": [
    "Webshop is an interactive web environment designed to mimic online shopping experiences, testing an agent's ability to navigate and assist in ecommerce tasks.",
    "Webshop comprising approximately 250 test cases.",
    "ToolQuery evaluates an agent's skills in using tools to retrieve and process information across domains.",
    "ToolQuery features 60 test cases across three distinct settings: Weather, Movie, and Academia.",
    "We use the testing configurations of AgentBoard (Ma et al., 2024) with Success Rate and Progress Rate for both Webshop and ToolQuery."
  ]
}